      "title": "Supreme Court extends travel ban on Mahinda and Basil",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Supreme Court has extended the travel ban imposed on former President Mahinda Rajapaksa and former minister Basil Rajapaksa until August 02, as they were named as respondents in a case filed over the economic crisis."
